	<p>Repost:<blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />I'm thinking along two lines on this.<br />
<br />
Either they modified crits to have a significant aggro modifier (Damage * number. Possibly 1.25-2?), or they modified any form of damage over X amount to add extra aggro. Like, say, a 500 damage hit would add a little bit more aggro, 1000 a moderate amount, 1500 a large chunk, 2000 means homicide.<hr size="1" /></blockquote>Was just tossing out numbers as an example, but I think you get the idea.  We haven't logged in as Dal and Cat to test anything yet, though.<br />
