	<p>Has aggro generation been moved to message generation?<br />
<br />
Perhaps arrow shots are being treated as both melee (fixed aggro per swing?) and nukes (aggro dependent on damage, or maybe max damage).<br />
<br />
Perhaps critical hits are adding their hate twice, and critical spells triple, because of the multiple messages.<br />
<br />
I would be particularly amused if crits were generating aggro *for every person that sees the crit message*. OK everyone, crits off, /serverfilter on  <img src="images/smilies/tongue.gif" border="0" alt="" title="stick out tongue" smilieid="6" /> .<br />
<br />
Testing would be easiest with a shadowknight, assuming their fixed hate generation spells are working properly.</p>
	
	
	
