	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I was begining to think that the extra agro was in some way linked to the message (ie. Double damage message generates 2x agro. Crit on top of this is an additional multiplier, but GrandTheft's post sorta killed that.<br />
<br />
Will have to log on my Rogue and test as well. Could be a lot harder duoing with my wife's Cleric now (She normally tanks because she can keep the agro.)<br />
<br />
<br />
<i>edit</i><br />
<br />
Oh, just got this from Graffe's. It would appear that all hate reduction spells are not reducing hate. This would explain why Jolt appears to be ineffective. <blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>'Rombus</b><br /><i><br />
Calm yourselves. All aggro reduction spells are messed up at the moment (as in, they don't seem to work at all). Other duration spells that reduce aggro or have a chance to wipe hate are wiping it 100% of the time. The emergency patch will come and fix it... hopefully. </i><hr size="1" /></blockquote></p>
	
	
	
	
