	<p>One thing of note.<br />
In the past, dying would equate to hatelist wipe, you are afterall a smear on the ground. However, this now no longer seems to be true. For example, raid engages with "Ubar_01", ranger waits, then goes into Archery mode and summarily wiped. Ranger is then ressed, loots his corpse, "ubar_01" is now at less then 50% , in any other circumstance one can safely assume that the ranger is now not even in the list right? Wrong. After looting, ranger goes full bore archery and again gets summoned even though the tank that has been beating on "ubar_01" hasn't died yet? Now that is just simply wrong.<br />
<br />
Possible Aggro transference from Cleric ress?</p>
	
	
	
