It would also follow that if EVERYONE got their own list identical to the warriors you could be at the top of your list simultaneously with the MT.  <br />
<br />
The MT cant taunt to the top of the list because he isnt in your list.  Then having lower hps/ac makes you look like a better target than the Warrior, thus you get smeared first.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
